    "description": "《棒！音乐》是一个新手友好的音乐创作工具 &amp; 作曲入门课程。从零开始，写下你的第一首歌吧——！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超容易上手的音乐创作工具</h2>我们提供了一套简单清晰的音乐创作工具，内置了超过 20 种性格各异的音色！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358190/extras/c41ddfd16f561db727e78f848b958dfc.poster.avif?t=1683613924\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358190/extras/c41ddfd16f561db727e78f848b958dfc.webm?t=1683613924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358190/extras/c41ddfd16f561db727e78f848b958dfc.mp4?t=1683613924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >和你的小动物乐手一起，演奏！</h2>每一种音色都由一个特定的小动物演奏，创作完成之后——和你的乐队一起演出吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358190/extras/89e545cb3a54c9a511b23fb831998981.poster.avif?t=1683613924\" width=598 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358190/extras/89e545cb3a54c9a511b23fb831998981.webm?t=1683613924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358190/extras/89e545cb3a54c9a511b23fb831998981.mp4?t=1683613924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从零开始的实用音乐创作指南</h2>为了让你能写出自己的第一首歌，我们设计了 8 节乐理课程。<br>抛弃艰深晦涩的书本理论，我们边做边学！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358190/extras/7f6d5dc54c59478a3f9434499b1752cc.poster.avif?t=1683613924\" width=599 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358190/extras/7f6d5dc54c59478a3f9434499b1752cc.webm?t=168